.about-home__wrapper
    .container 
        .about-home__text-wrapper
            %h3 I'm Nicole, a designer and front end developer from Dominican Republic, based in New York.
            %p
                I specialize in Graphic and UX/UI Design and Front End Development. In over 6 years I've worked with a range of clients across wellness, finance, tech, and entertainment. Because I understand both sides of the process, I create work that is as thoughtful as it is functional. I bring a meticulous eye, a love for experimentation, and a commitment to creating work that is engaging, and leaves a lasting impression. 
            .btn__wrapper
                = link_to "Get to Know Me", "/about", :class => "btn"
